       fecha_cita='2019-11-04' and   
       codconsulta='01'  and 
       asistido=3 and
       a.codclien not in (Select codclien from MFactura where fechafac='2019-11-04') and
       a.codclien not in (Select codclien from MSSMFact where fechafac='2019-11-04')  and
       a.codclien not in (
       select codclien  from cma_MFactura where  fechafac='2019-11-04' and  numfactu  in  (Select numfactu from cma_DFactura where  cod_subgrupo='SUEROTERAPIA'  ))
